## Scopes on Associations

```ruby
class User < ApplicationRecord
  has_many :articles
  has_many :published_articles, 
           -> { where(status: 'published') },
           class_name: 'Article'
  has_many :recent_articles,
           -> { where('created_at > ?', 1.week.ago).order(created_at: :desc) },
           class_name: 'Article'
end
```

**Usage:**
```ruby
user = User.first
user.articles            # All articles
user.published_articles  # Only published
user.recent_articles     # Only recent
```

